  "description": "# Tropical Nights RCP 8.5\n\nThis dataset provides information on the number of tropical nights under the RCP 4.5 climate scenario.\n\n## Data Structure\nThe data includes mean and standard deviation of tropical nights for different decades and months, categorized by tourism region and elevation.\n\n## Visualization\nSelect a region and elevation on the map to view the time series of tropical nights from 1951 to 2100.\n",
